  </section>

  <!-- About Us / Our Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Building transparency and accessibility in Swiss relocation services
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl border border-gray-200">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            ReloFinder was born from a simple observation: the Swiss relocation market was complex, fragmented, and often opaque. International professionals and companies struggled to find reliable information, compare services, or connect with the right providers for their specific needs.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            We are a team of relocation experts, technology professionals, and Swiss market specialists with decades of combined experience. Our team has helped thousands of individuals and companies successfully navigate the complexities of relocating to Switzerland — from visa processes and housing searches to health insurance and settling-in services.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            What sets us apart is our commitment to transparency and accessibility. We don't just list service providers; we curate, verify, and continuously evaluate our network to ensure you have access to the best relocation professionals Switzerland has to offer. Whether you're an individual professional, an HR department managing international transfers, or a multinational corporation optimizing your global mobility program, ReloFinder is your trusted partner.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Our platform leverages technology to make the relocation process more efficient, while maintaining the personal touch and expert guidance that makes all the difference when moving to a new country. We understand that relocation is not just about logistics — it's about starting a new chapter of your life or career with confidence and clarity.
          </p>

          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 mt-8">
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              <strong class="text-gray-900">Our commitment:</strong> To continuously improve and expand our platform, working tirelessly to make Swiss relocation services more accessible, transparent, and efficient for everyone.
